          "settings": {
            "heading": "Return and Refund Policy",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>At Zinara, your satisfaction is our highest priority. We strive to ensure every purchase brings you joy and confidence. In the rare case that your experience falls short, we offer a transparent and hassle-free return and refund process.</p><h2><strong>Return Window</strong></h2><ul><li><strong>18KT Gold Vermeil Jewellery:</strong> 7-Day Return Policy<br/><br/></li><li><strong>Gold Jewellery:</strong> 15-Day Return Policy<br/><br/></li></ul><p>You may return your product for <em>any reason</em> within the applicable window.</p><p><strong>Important:<br/></strong>For any <strong>missing item in the shipment</strong>, you must notify us <strong>within 24 hours</strong> of delivery.</p><h2><strong>Eligibility for Returns & Refunds</strong></h2><p>Our return and refund policy applies <strong>only to orders placed on</strong><a href=\"http://www.zinara.in\"><strong> </strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>www.zinara.in</strong></span></a>.</p><p>To ensure a smooth return process, please ensure:</p><ol><li>The jewellery is <strong>unused, unworn, and in its original condition</strong>, with all tags attached.<br/><br/></li><li>All <strong>original packaging</strong>, including boxes, pouches, and certificates, is returned.<br/><br/></li><li>The <strong>original invoice/receipt</strong> or proof of purchase is provided.<br/><br/></li><li>Any <strong>complimentary gifts</strong> or free products received with the order are returned with the main item.</li></ol><h3><strong>Unboxing Video</strong></h3><p>Please record a <strong>complete unboxing video</strong> when opening your package.<br/> This helps our team verify and resolve issues related to:</p><ul><li>Missing items<br/><br/></li><li>Damaged items<br/><br/></li><li>Wrong product received<br/></li></ul><p>Requests without an unboxing video may face delays or limitations.</p><h2><strong>Non-Returnable Items</strong></h2><p>The following items <strong>cannot</strong> be returned, cancelled, or refunded:</p><ul><li>Customised, personalised, engraved, or made-to-order jewellery<br/><br/></li><li>Products showing physical damage, wear, or alterations<br/><br/></li><li>Products that have been washed or tampered with<br/><br/></li><li>Items not returned in original condition with packaging, tags, invoice & certificates<br/><br/></li><li>Any package where the contents returned do not match the products claimed<br/><br/></li></ul><p>If you are unsure about eligibility, contact us at <strong>help@zinara.in</strong> or WhatsApp <strong>+91-9211633248</strong>.</p><h1><strong>Return Process</strong></h1><h3><strong>1. Submit a Request</strong></h3><p>Email or WhatsApp our support team.<br/> Our team will generate a <strong>case ticket/ID</strong> and review your request.</p><h3><strong>2. Receive the Shipping Label</strong></h3><p>Within 48 hours, you will receive a <strong>fully insured return shipping label</strong>.</p><h3><strong>3. Pack the Jewellery</strong></h3><ul><li>Use the <strong>original packaging<br/><br/></strong></li><li>Include the <strong>certificate</strong>, invoice, and all accessories<br/><br/></li><li>Bubble-wrap the product securely<br/><br/></li><li>Hand it over to the logistics partner assigned<br/><br/></li></ul><h3><strong>4. Inspection</strong></h3><p>Once received, your product will undergo a <strong>quality check</strong>.</p><p>Zinara reserves the right to:</p><ul><li>Evaluate the returned product<br/><br/></li><li>Reject returns that do not meet eligibility<br/><br/></li><li>Deduct the <strong>full MRP</strong> for any missing item (including free gifts)<br/><br/></li></ul><h3><strong>5. Refund Authorization</strong></h3><p>If approved, your refund will be processed.</p><h1><strong>Refund Modes & Timelines</strong></h1><p><strong>Order Type - Refund Mode Timeline*</strong></p><p><strong>Cash on Delivery (COD) - 10–15 days</strong> from authorization</p><p><strong>Prepaid Orders - 7 days</strong> from authorization</p><p>*Additional time may be required by your bank or card issuer. Zinara is not responsible for such delays.</p><h1><strong>Cases Where Returns Cannot Be Accepted</strong></h1><p>We will not accept return or replacement requests for:</p><ul><li>Products with <strong>physical damage</strong>, missing stones, scratches, dents, or signs of use<br/><br/></li><li>Products <strong>not in original condition<br/><br/></strong></li><li>Products returned <strong>without packaging, invoice, certificate, or tags<br/><br/></strong></li><li>Products with <strong>tampered or unreadable serial numbers<br/><br/></strong></li><li><strong>Customised or personalised jewellery<br/><br/></strong></li><li>Products purchased under <strong>special offers, promotions, or clearance<br/><br/></strong></li><li>Return shipments where the <strong>number of items does not match</strong> what was declared</li></ul><h1><strong>Need Help?</strong></h1><p>If you’re unsure about the eligibility of your item or need assistance with a return:<br/> Mail: <strong>help@zinara.in<br/></strong> WhatsApp: <strong>+91-9211633248</strong></p><p>We’re here to make your Zinara experience exceptional :)</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
